## Memory & Task Tracking
- Project memory is stored in [.agent-memory/](file://./.agent-memory/). Read [.agent-memory/INDEX.md](file://./.agent-memory/INDEX.md) before starting.
- Keep architectural findings, issues, and resolutions logged in [.agent-memory/project.md](file://./.agent-memory/project.md).
- Follow the **작업 메모리 기록 및 분류 규칙 (Memory Logs & Classification)** in `AGENTS.md` whenever you complete a task or discover new behavior.

## Working Principles
1. **Surgical Edits**: Make precise, minimum-disruption changes. Avoid refactoring unrelated code.
2. **Examine First**: Verify file structure and read existing code before writing new code.
3. **No Secrets**: Never commit API keys, tokens, or credentials. Use environment variables.
